<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= @school_name || "SNB Convent School" %> - Welcome</title>
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag 'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@400;700&family=Roboto+Slab:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/4.7.0/css/font-awesome.min.css">
    <script src="http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js" type="text/javascript"></script>
    <style>
        .main-content {
            flex-grow: 1; 
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        h2, h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        /* --- Hero Section --- */
        .admissions-hero {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 60px 20px;
            background-color: var(--card-background);
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--secondary-color);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .admissions-hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #555;
            margin-bottom: 25px;
        }

        /* --- Buttons (Reused from Welcome/Discover More) --- */
        .btn-primary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 30px;
            background-color: transparent;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s, color 0.3s;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
        }

        /* --- 4-Step Process Section --- */
        .admissions-process {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            background-color: var(--card-background);
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .step-container {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            justify-content: space-between;
        }

        .step {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border: 1px dashed #ced4da;
            border-radius: 6px;
            transition: transform 0.3s, box-shadow 0.3s;
        }

        .step:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .step-number {
            display: block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            line-height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin: 0 auto 15px;
        }

        .step h4 {
            color: var(--secondary-color);
            font-family: var(--font-heading);
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        /* --- Requirements Section --- */
        .admissions-requirements {
            padding: 40px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            border-radius: 8px;
        }

        .requirements-flex {
            display: flex;
            gap: 40px;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .requirements-list, .important-dates {
            background-color: var(--card-background);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
        }

        .requirements-list {
            flex: 2;
        }

        .important-dates {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .requirements-list ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .requirements-list li {
            padding: 10px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px dotted #e9ecef;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .important-dates h4 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .date-item {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);
        }

        /* --- FAQ/CTA Section --- */
        .admissions-faq {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 30px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .admissions-faq a {
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        /* --- Responsive Adjustments --- */
        @media (max-width: 992px) {
            .step-container, .requirements-flex {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 20px;
            }
            .step {
                max-width: 100%;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .admissions-hero h2 {
                font-size: 1.8rem;
            }
            .admissions-faq a {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px auto;
                width: 80%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header class="main-header">
        <nav class="navbar">
            <div class="logo">
                <h1><%= @school_name || "SNB Convent School" %></h1>
            </div>

            <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="icon" onclick="toggleMenu()">
                <i class="fa fa-bars"></i>
            </a>

            <ul id="myLinks" class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="<%= root_path %>">Home</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admission">Admissions</a></li>
                <li><a href="/academic">Academics</a></li>
                <li><a href="/contact">Contact Us</a></li>
                <li><a href="/admin">Portal Login</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <main class="main-content">
        
        <section class="admissions-hero">
            <h2>Welcome to SNB Convent School Admissions</h2>
            <p>Your journey to a brighter future starts here. Follow the steps below to apply for the upcoming academic year.</p>
            <a href="#process" class="btn btn-primary">Start Your Application</a>
        </section>

        <section id="process" class="admissions-process">
            <h3>Our 4-Step Admissions Process</h3>
            
            <div class="step-container">
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">1</span>
                    <h4>Review & Inquire</h4>
                    <p>Read our admission policies and complete the **Online Inquiry Form**. This helps us understand your needs and send you relevant materials.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">2</span>
                    <h4>Submit Application</h4>
                    <p>Complete the full **Online Application** and pay the non-refundable application fee. Upload all required documents (transcripts, etc.).</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">3</span>
                    <h4>Interview & Assessment</h4>
                    <p>Schedule a mandatory **Student Interview** and complete any required academic assessments or entrance exams.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-number">4</span>
                    <h4>Decision & Enrollment</h4>
                    <p>Receive your admission decision. Upon acceptance, complete the **Enrollment Contract** and pay the deposit to secure your spot.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="admissions-requirements">
            <h3>Required Application Documents</h3>
            <div class="requirements-flex">
                <div class="requirements-list">
                    <h4>Essential Paperwork</h4>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Completed Online Application Form</li>
                        <li>Non-refundable Application Fee ($100)</li>
                        <li>Official Transcript/Report Cards (Last 2 years)</li>
                        <li>Copy of Birth Certificate or Passport</li>
                        <li>Two Letters of Recommendation (from teachers)</li>
                    </ul>
                    <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Download Checklist PDF</a>
                </div>
                <div class="important-dates">
                    <h4>Key Dates</h4>
                    <p class="date-item">Application Opens: **October 1st**</p>
                    <p class="date-item">Priority Deadline: **January 15th**</p>
                    <p class="date-item">Decisions Mailed: **March 1st**</p>
                    <p class="date-item">Enrollment Deadline: **April 15th**</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="admissions-faq">
            <h3>Questions?</h3>
            <p>Our Admissions Office is here to help. Contact us directly or view our Frequently Asked Questions.</p>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Admissions FAQ</a>
            <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">Contact Admissions Office</a>
        </section>

    </main>

    <footer class="main-footer">
        <p>&copy; <%= Time.now.year %> SNB Convent School. All Rights Reserved. | Address: 123 School Rd | Phone: (555) 123-4567</p>
    </footer>
    <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track': 'reload' %>
</body>
</html>